msgstr "%1$s 在 r==%2$s"

msgid "Cauchy prior width"
msgstr "Cauchy 先驗寬度"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that group 1 is greater "
"than group 2."
msgstr "對於所有檢定，對立假設指定第 1 組大於第 2 組。"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the mean is greater "
"than 0."
msgstr "對於所有檢定，對立假設指定平均數大於 0。"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that measure 1 is "
"greater than measure 2."
msgstr "對於所有檢定，對立假設指定測量 1 大於測量 2。"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that group 1 is less "
"than group 2."
msgstr "對於所有檢定，對立假設指定第 1 組小於第 2 組。"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the mean is less "
"than 0."
msgstr "對於所有檢定，對立假設指定平均數小於 0。"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that measure 1 is less "
"than measure 2."
msgstr "對於所有檢定，對立假設指定測量 1 小於測量 2。"

msgid "Bayesian One Sample T-Test"
msgstr "貝氏單一樣本 T 檢定"

msgid "Bayesian Paired Samples T-Test"
msgstr "貝氏成對樣本 T 檢定"

msgid "Not enough observations."
msgstr "觀測數不足。"

msgid "Model Summary"
msgstr "模型摘要"

msgid "Effect size"
msgstr "效果量"

msgid "Standard error"
msgstr "標準誤"

msgid "Max %1$s"
msgstr "最大 %1$s"

msgid "Default %1$s"
msgstr "預設 %1$s"

msgid "exp(Effect size)"
msgstr "exp（效果量）"

msgid "Bayes Factor Robustness Plot"
msgstr "貝氏因子穩健性圖"

msgid "Bayes factor contours breaks could not be parsed into numbers."
msgstr "貝氏因子等高線中斷值無法解析為數字。"

msgid "Bayes factor contours breaks must be positive."
msgstr "貝氏因子等高線中斷值必須為正數。"

msgid "Bayes factor contours breaks must be increasing."
msgstr "貝氏因子等高線中斷值必須遞增。"

msgid "exp(Prior mean)"
msgstr "exp(先驗平均數)"

msgid "Prior mean"
msgstr "先驗平均數"

msgid "Prior standard deviation"
msgstr "先驗標準差"

msgid ""
"The default Bayes factor is based on unit information prior corresponding to "
"a %1$s effect size, a normal distribution with mean = 0 and sd = %2$s."
msgstr ""
"預設貝氏因子係基於單位資訊先驗，對應於 %1$s 效果量，即平均數 = 0、標準差 = "
"%2$s 之常態分配。"

msgid "Bayesian Binomial Test"
msgstr "貝氏二項式檢定"

msgid ""
"- *Bayes factor*: If one-sided test is requested:\n"
"  - BF+0: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the one-sided "
"alternative hypothesis that the population mean is larger than the test "
"value\n"
"  - BF-0: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the one-sided "
"alternative hypothesis that the population mean is smaller than the test "
"value\n"
"- BF0+: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the null hypothesis "
"relative to the one-sided alternative hypothesis that the population mean is "
"larger than the test value\n"
"- BF0-: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the null hypothesis "
"relative to the one-sided alternative hypothesis that that the population "
"mean is smaller than the test value\n"
"  - **p**: p-value corresponding to t-statistic."
msgstr ""

