msgstr "無法檢定檢定值大於 1 之假設。"

msgid "Cannot test the hypothesis that the test value is less than 0."
msgstr "無法檢定檢定值小於 0 之假設。"

msgid "Undefined hypothesis"
msgstr "未定義之假設"

